input: Objective: Access a bookmarked page in Chrome
output:
To safely access a bookmarked page in Google Chrome, follow these steps:

1. Open Google Chrome on your computer.
2. Click on the three dots (vertical ellipsis) in the upper-right corner of the browser window to open the menu.
3. Hover over "Bookmarks" in the dropdown menu.
4. Select "Bookmark Manager" from the list. This will open a new tab with all your bookmarks listed.
5. Find and click on the bookmark you want to access. The corresponding page will open in a new tab.
